OL,6,FTwo killers who hunted down a father-
OL,7,Fof-one on bicycles before stabbing him
OL,8,Fto death to "settle a score" over
OL,9,Fdrugs have been jailed for life.
OL,11,FDaneiko Ferguson, 27, was attacked by
OL,12,FAlga Lutondo and Halgon Randon in
OL,13,FCompton Road, Harehills, Leeds, in the
OL,14,Fearly hours of 16 February last year.
OL,16,FThe pair set out on a revenge mission
OL,17,Fafter being told that Mr Ferguson had
OL,18,Fstolen some drugs from one of their
OL,19,Fassociates, Leeds Crown Court heard.
