OL,4,Cbicycles jailed for life
OL,6,FThey stabbed him five times, including
OL,7,Fa fatal injury to his groin.
OL,9,FMr Ferguson was found by a passing
OL,10,Ftaxi driver and taken to hospital but
OL,11,Fdied a short time later.
OL,13,FAn investigation found Lutondo, 33,
OL,14,Fhad enlisted Randon to carry out the
OL,15,Fattack. The pair trawled the area on
OL,16,Fbikes before finding Mr Ferguson.
OL,18,FLutondo was arrested at Heathrow
OL,19,FAirport as he tried to leave the
OL,20,Fcountry after the attack.
