OL,4,Cbicycles jailed for life
OL,6,FHe was found guilty of murder
OL,7,Ffollowing a trial in December. Randon,
OL,8,F44, was convicted after a retrial last
OL,9,Fmonth.
OL,11,FLutondo, of Berkeley Crescent,
OL,12,FHarehills, was jailed for a minimum of
OL,13,F28 years. Randon, of Brown Hill
OL,14,FTerrace, Harehills, was given a
OL,15,Fminimum term of 26 years.
OL,17,F'I will never forgive or forget'
OL,19,FIn a statement, Mr Ferguson's mother
OL,20,FHazel Clamp said she suffered
OL,21,F"constant panic attacks".
