OL,6,F"The impact this has had on the family
OL,7,Fas a whole can be seen daily," she
OL,8,Fsaid.
OL,10,F"We have no enjoyment anymore, we just
OL,11,Flive to exist."
OL,13,FShe said her son's 10-year-old
OL,14,Fdaughter and family and friends had
OL,15,Fbeen left "heartbroken beyond belief".
OL,17,FShe added: "These two individuals
OL,18,Fcaused immense suffering to my son
OL,19,Fthat night and left him to bleed to
OL,20,Fdeath without a thought of anyone else
OL,21,Fbut themselves.
