OL,6,F"The thought of what was going through
OL,7,Fmy son's head on those last few
OL,8,Fmoments of his life will haunt me
OL,9,Fforever. I believe that he called out
OL,10,Ffor me as I woke at the time of his
OL,11,Fpassing, with a very strange feeling.
OL,12,FI didn't get the chance to hold his
OL,13,Fhand and say goodbye. I will never
OL,14,Fforgive or forget the actions of the
OL,15,Fthree of them that night."
