OL,6,FDet Ch Insp Damian Roebuck, of West
OL,7,FYorkshire Police, said: "Lutondo and
OL,8,FRandon are clearly dangerous
OL,9,Findividuals who were prepared to use
OL,10,Fextreme violence to settle a score
OL,11,Fwithout any consideration for the
OL,12,Fconsequences.
OL,14,F"We hope their convictions and
OL,15,Fimprisonment for Daneiko's murder will
OL,16,Fgive at least some small measure of
OL,17,Fcomfort to his family as they continue
OL,18,Fto deal with the pain and heartbreak
OL,19,Fthey are going through."
